########################################################### 
rtmrun
###########################################################

Øystein Godøy, METNO/FOU, 2013-12-11 

PURPOSE
A Perl wrapper around libRadtran (version of choice) that simplifies
configuration and operation of libRadtran when doing experiments. It can
be used to perform simulations for a specific location and time period and
supports aggregation of output in files suitable for further processing in
e.g. Matlab, R or similar.

LICENSE
Check LICENSE file.

COMMENTS
The code is not fully working for AVHRR simulation yet.
